item.title: Why cnt i freeking log on?
item.dc:creator: @nappymonster nappymonster
item.description:
@nappymonster wrote:

If you are using wireless internet, go to start>>Run and type cmd
Now type ipconfig

Look for numbers that are the same or similar to 192.168.2.1

Type the number into an adress bar

Go to port forwarding/virtual servers

Call it moparscape

Open the port 43594

Done!

Try that. If not just keep searching for a server, the first server i ever connected to was about my 20th attempt.

Nappymonster
